data.description: This BEAUTIFUL brick home has so much to offer! The exterior of this property features a fenced back yard, partially fenced front yard, a double lot, metal roof, RV/ boat garage, full exterior camera security system, 2 car carport and more! This home was a 3 bed 1.5 bath recently converted to a 2 bath with many new updates. The cozy living area has a very homey feel with a fireplace. The kitchen has a retro feel with a modern touch. This home has a formal dining area with plenty of space for family gatherings. Schedule a tour today to see this beauty!
